
=Description=

This organizational model of [[Open Value Network]]s instantiates commons-based peer production. The model emerged from practice, within the [http://www.sensorica.co SENSORICA] community and network. To know more, see the main [[Open Value Network]] page, or go to the [http://valuenetwork.referata.com/wiki/Main_Page OVN wiki].

=More Information=

See our report on open and contributive accounting, with a case study of Sensorica, via:

* Report: [[Value in the Commons Economy]]: Developments in Open and Contributory Value Accounting. By Michel Bauwens and Vasilis Niaros. Heinrich Boll Foundation, 2016.
[https://www.boell.de/en/2017/02/01/value-commons-economy-developments-open-and-contributory-value-accounting]

